description: "This map's cartouche features an illustration of three men bowing before an enthroned ruler. A second image is of a procession where a horned four-armed humanoid creature is being carried on poles by two bearers, while musicians follow behind."
label: "Asiae recentissima delineatio, qua status et imperia totius orientis unacum orientalibus Indiis exhibentur / authore Ioh: Bapt: Homanno s.c.m. geographo."
